213
00:16:20,513 --> 00:16:23,233
Nie, toto je jediný spôsob.

214
00:16:25,606 --> 00:16:27,999
Baek Woo Jin! Baek Woo Jin!

215
00:16:32,017 --> 00:16:34,504
